NOORSOB
v.
SUPREME COURT of NC 131P16-5 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 10, 2017 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney Geneal, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Somchoi Noonsab, For Noonsab, Somchoi. Somchoi Noorsob, For Noorsob, Somchoi.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 9th of March 2017 by Petitioner to Default in the Matters of Denied Writ of Habeas Corpus:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 10th of March 2017."
